category: LOOK IN THE CABINET
category comment: 

clue: The Judiciary Act of 1789 created this Cabinet job

response: Attorney General

clue: In 1981 the Maritime Administration was transferred from Commerce to this Cabinet department

response: Department of Transportation

clue: The first Cabinet secretary in the line of presidential succession

response: the Secretary of State

clue: The secretary of this newest Cabinet department is last in the order of presidential succession, behind Veterans Affairs

response: Homeland Security

clue: At the time of its establishment in 1849, this Cabinet department was also known as the Home Department

response: the Department of the Interior

